OL,3,CDavina McCall is recovering in the ICU
OL,4,Cafter surgery for 'rare' brain tumour
OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew spoke to neurosurgeons about the
OL,8,Fprocedure Davina McCall underwent this
OL,9,Fafternoon
OL,11,FDavina McCall is out of surgery and
OL,12,Frecovering in the ICU after revealing
OL,13,Fshe had "very rare" brain tumour.
OL,15,FIn an Instagram post by her husband
OL,16,FMichael Douglas, he said: "Davina is
OL,17,Fout of surgery and according to the
OL,18,Fsurgeon it was textbook!
OL,20,F"She's currently recovering in the ICU
OL,21,Fas a precaution.
