OL,3,CDavina McCall is recovering in the ICU
OL,4,Cafter surgery for 'rare' brain tumour
OL,6,F"As you can imagine she's utterly
OL,7,Fexhausted.
OL,9,F"Thanks so much for all the love from
OL,10,Feveryone on here... it's powerful
OL,11,Fstuff, we are super grateful."
OL,13,FIn an earlier Instagram video on
OL,14,FFriday, the TV presenter asked her
OL,15,Ffans to "say a prayer" for her as she
OL,16,Fprepared for surgery to remove the
OL,17,Fbenign tumour, known as a colloid cyst.
