OL,3,CDavina McCall is recovering in the ICU
OL,4,Cafter surgery for 'rare' brain tumour
OL,6,FAddressing her followers, she said: "A
OL,7,Ffew months ago I did a menopause talk
OL,8,Ffor a company and they offered me a
OL,9,Fhealth scan in return which I thought
OL,10,FI was going to ace. It turns out I had
OL,11,Fa benign brain tumour called a colloid
OL,12,Fcyst which is very rare, three in a
OL,13,Fmillion."
OL,15,F"I slightly put my head in the sand
OL,16,Ffor a while, then I saw quite a few
OL,17,Fneurosurgeons and I realised that I
OL,18,Fhave to get it taken out," she added.
