OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe 'My Mum, Your Dad' host said she
OL,12,Fwould be having a craniotomy to remove
OL,13,Fthe 14-millimetre-wide tumour.
OL,15,FJoined in the video by her partner
OL,16,FMichael Douglas, the 57-year-old said:
OL,17,F"Say a prayer for me. I'm in good
OL,18,Fspirits."
