OL,3,CDavina McCall is recovering in the ICU
OL,4,Cafter surgery for 'rare' brain tumour
OL,6,FShe continued: "I'm okay, it's been up
OL,7,Fand down obviously. We've been through
OL,8,Fa lot."
OL,10,FMcCall said her recovery in hospital
OL,11,Fwould last nine days and she will be
OL,12,Foff her phone while she recovers at
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,FShe said: "I don't want you to worry
OL,16,Fabout me, I'm doing enough as it is.
OL,17,FI'll see you on the other side."
