OL,6,FA spokesperson for The Brain Tumour
OL,7,FCharity said: "Our Support Team has
OL,8,Fbeen providing Davina with information
OL,9,Fand reassurance - in confidence - in
OL,10,Fthe lead up to her surgery."
OL,12,FThey added: "As an inspiration to so
OL,13,Fmany, we're grateful that Davina has
OL,14,Fchosen to raise awareness of this
OL,15,Funique devastating disease."
